import React, {useState} from 'react' const Register = () => { const initail = { firstname: '', lastname: '', email: '', password: '', confirmpassword: '', } const [allentry, setallentry] = useState([]) const handleSubmit = (e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); const entries = { firstname: initail.firstname, lastname: initail.lastname, email: initail.email, password: initail.password, confirmpassword: initail.confirmpassword, } setallentry(...allentry, entries) } return ( <>
{ return initail.firstname = e.target.value }} />
) } export default Register;
